Name: bam2fasta
Version: 1.0.8
Summary: tool for converting a bam file to fastas
Home-page: https://github.com/czbiohub/bam2fasta
Author: Pranathi Vemuri
Author-email: pranathi93.vemuri@gmail.com
Maintainer: Pranathi Vemuri
